description: It’s always nice to have a nice, relaxing massage - but Chase’s massage turned out to be tickle torment instead. Chase Lachance came in for a massage, but when he fell asleep on the massage table he woke up to find himself bound and naked. Then the tickle torment started on Chase’s ultra-ticklish naked body from his sensitive soles to his exposed and ticklish balls. No spot on his helpless body was spared from his armpits to his feet. This tickling nightmare goes on and on and all Chase can do is laugh hysterically.
title: Chase's Ticklish Massage
